    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"struggle\" feels so heavy when u think about it. like, we spend our whole lives working, hurting, and trying to find meaning, only for the sun to explode and all of it to be erased. it feels like participating in a play where you know the theater is going to burn down in the end. it just seems so exhausting to keep pretending it matters, you know? like we're all just performing for an empty room.",
